@pmbenjamin Just finished another video on array deconstruction, which cleans up the code above to just:

```

function lookUp(firstName, prop){
  let [contact] = contacts.filter(x => x.firstName === firstName )
  return contact === undefined ? "No such contact" : contact[prop] != null ? contact[prop] : "No such property"
}

```
